<body><h2>Lot's 'o Hemp Links</h2>
<IMG SRC="images/rules/linecolo.gif"><p>
<h4>This is list of sites I found with Webcrawler and Lycos searches a long
time ago. Most of them seem to have gone dead. I don't really have the time to 
do an overhaul on this page, so I suggest that you hop on over to 
<a href="http://www.altavista.digital.com/">Altavista</a> and do a search there.</h4>
<h2><a href="http://altavista.digital.com/">Search Altavista<img border=0 hspace=5 src="http://www.olywa.net/images/alta.gif"></a></h2>
