-7,1983. 5. Cancellieri, V., Fara, G.M., J. Inf.Dis. (151)3, pp482-484, 1985. 6. Tagiliabue, A., et.al., Clin ExpImmunol 62, pp242-247, 1985. 7. D&#178;Amelio, R., et. Al., InfectImmun 56, pp 2731-2735, 1988. 8. Kantele, A., Vaccine 8, pp 321-326,1990. 9. Kantele, A., M&aacute;kel&aacute;, P.H., Vaccine 9, pp423-427, 1991.</P></BODY></HTML>
