<HEAD>
<TITLE>DOE EREN - EE Mission Statement </TITLE>

</HEAD>
<BODY bgcolor="#FFFFFF" vlink="#843131" text="#000000" link="#323294">

<center>
<a href="/cgi-bin/imagemap.cgi/picts/eren.map"><img src="/picts/eren.gif" ISMAP border=0></a>
<H1>EE Mission Statement
</H1>
<IMG SRC="/picts/topbar.gif">
</center>
<BR>

     The mission of the Office of Energy Efficiency and Renewable Energy is
     to lead the Nation to a stronger economy, a cleaner environment and a
     more secure future through development and deployment of sustainable
     energy technologies.<P>
<BR>
<IMG SRC="/picts/erenbar.gif">
